Key Match Events: Emilio Nsue scored a hat-trick for Equatorial Guinea with goals in the 21st, 51st, and 61st minutes.
Jorge Miranda Boacho scored for Equatorial Guinea in the 46th minute.
Emilio Obiang Obono scored an own goal for Guinea-Bissau in the 37th minute.
Jorginho Correia scored for Guinea-Bissau in the 93rd minute.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match was part of the Africa Cup of Nations Group A.
The match took place at Stade Olympique Alassane Ouattara.
The attendance for the match was 13,888.
